  m_Name: Tut_ClueNote2_Page1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  type: 0
  text: "I don\u2019t know how long I\u2019ve been here anymore. Time bends in this
    place\u2026 or maybe I\u2019ve stopped counting.\n\nIf you\u2019re reading this,
    then you\u2019ve made it further than I did.\n\nDon\u2019t trust the silence
    of the maze. It listens. It waits. The darkness between the walls is not empty
    something moves in it. Not always seen, never fully understood\u2026 but always
    near when the light fades.\n\nI tried to map it.I tried to understand its pattern.There
    aren't any.Only shifting paths that change when you're not looking"
  texture: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fe28bf42f38b7c44d8174dffa2650480, type: 3}
